Took reference from Book Head First Java.

To compile : ant -buildfile src/build.xml all


To Run     : ant -buildfile src/build.xml run -Darg0=/import/linux1/home1/mpancha1/Mpancha1_Fall_17/input.txt -Darg1=/import/linux1/home1/mpancha1/Mpancha1_Fall_17/output.txt -Darg2=4

1st arg : Input_file path
2nd arg : Output_file path
3rd arg : Debug Value 

Calculated Avg_Traffic_per_day and Avg_Prohibited_Item_per_day at every line and according to that setting states.